POCOX5 5G
Everything. Just right.
120Hz FHD+ AMOLED DotDisplay
Snapdragon® 695 processor
33W fast charging
48MP Al triple camera
6.67" AMOLED DotDisplay
For outstanding visuals
POCO X5 5G features a sleek 120Hz AMOLED display, standing out from the competition. Enjoy rich visuals and performance with better power consumption.
120Hz refresh rate
Smoother and quicker
SGS-certified, high-speed 120Hz refresh rate gives you a smoother gaming and viewing experience. 240Hz touch sampling ensures every moment gets counted.
Poco X5 5g
Super resolution touch
10 times more precision
A huge 10-times precision improvement gives touch control better accuracy than ever, for better game control and a smoother experience.

Low blue light display
Easier on the eyes.
The carefully calibrated display effectively reduces blue light and protects your eyes for lasting comfort.
Compact
Yet powerful
Extremely lightweight and thin, POCO X5 5G is equipped with a large 5000mAh battery, bringing high-performance and durability in a sleeker form.
The extra-large capacity 5000mAh battery perfectly fits the compact design of POCO X5 5G, giving long-lasting, reliable use*. Enjoy life to the max with a full charge!
Snapdragon® 695
Full of power
Built on TSMC's 6nm process and a new architecture, coupled with Cortex-A78, the Snapdragon® 695 delivers superior performance to meet your everyday needs.
